{"tid":343273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[職場初哥有問題] reference check","createTime":"2017-08-01T10:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T15:42:26.000Z","uid":132764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03f5f51a6dc3e53621643998755ae382c7d2ebea","tid":343273,"uid":132764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:08:03.000Z","msg":"岩岩畢業呢排搵緊工 但有部分既工要我填張reference check authorisation form<br />\n咁我就打去之前返工個度問人可唔可以幫我填啦(填既資料都係名呀，職位 email, contact number etc.)<br />\n點知佢覆我既係 除非你新僱主send email嚟，否則我唔可以幫你填<br />\n<br />\n問題嚟啦:<br />\n1. 我呢份form係嚟緊見既工send比我，要我interview個日填好帶埋過去，佢唔幫我填我點見工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 其實填嚟有乜用？我唔會咁蠢報流料昆9佢咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 佢唔肯填，我可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 第一次開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18c854f8bebd1d748df5d7a5be1f68e6602b16f","tid":343273,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:12:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee8532a9cb350fe98d27f3a91d3a67ef45b8ceef","tid":343273,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:13:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83ff05a18ad36f1df4f61e7958a0f2a4cf581595","tid":343273,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:15:34.000Z","msg":"份野係你填黎授權比佢check你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6dbb566e30ecc5bbd778f3ef25cda4bc63f8bc6","tid":343273,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:17:42.000Z","msg":"授左權先會揾你前公司check"},{"pid":"611c423cc97fb57ca4460c0247ebd53e22175e57","tid":343273,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩畢業呢排搵緊工 但有部分既工要我填張reference check authorisation form<br />\n咁我就打去之前返工個度問人可唔可以幫我填啦(填既資料都係名呀，職位 email, contact number etc.)<br />\n點知佢覆我既係 除非你新僱主send email嚟，否則我唔可以幫你填<br />\n<br />\n問題嚟啦:<br />\n1. 我呢份form係嚟緊見既工send比我，要我interview個日填好帶埋過去，佢唔幫我填我點見工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 其實填嚟有乜用？我唔會咁蠢報流料昆9佢咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 佢唔肯填，我可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 第一次開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴線點會問前僱主填 比得你ofc自己填啦<br />\n你應該問你前僱主可否用作reference <br />\n又或者出reference letter(如果你咁on9無攞過)"},{"pid":"76a7118f194d6f98974802cc78b71a6f7ae9de06","tid":343273,"uid":132764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T11:52:46.000Z","msg":"回大家:<br />\n其實我都仲係唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我係咪只係填左呢度，同埋簽個名比佢就得？<br />\n下面果啲唔洗我填？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/195233_d5a20b550377602db9cccd81d474d567.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F195233_d5a20b550377602db9cccd81d474d567.jpg&h=0f819550&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5626f12af3f138dc53e13eba7d27797d05d38398","tid":343273,"uid":132764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:28:11.000Z","msg":"Push下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b025d26fabf8822eaa1f54922fd83e99fcfb9a36","tid":343273,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回大家:<br />\n其實我都仲係唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我係咪只係填左呢度，同埋簽個名比佢就得？<br />\n下面果啲唔洗我填？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/195233_d5a20b550377602db9cccd81d474d567.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F195233_d5a20b550377602db9cccd81d474d567.jpg&h=0f819550&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n填埋下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}